gnutls_hmac(3)                                                                                    gnutls                                                                                    gnutls_hmac(3)

NAME
       gnutls_hmac - API function

SYNOPSIS
       #include <gnutls/crypto.h>

       int gnutls_hmac(gnutls_hmac_hd_t handle, const void * ptext, size_t ptext_len);

ARGUMENTS
       gnutls_hmac_hd_t handle
                   is a gnutls_hmac_hd_t type

       const void * ptext
                   the data to hash

       size_t ptext_len
                   the length of data to hash

DESCRIPTION
       This function will hash the given data using the algorithm specified by the context.

RETURNS
       Zero or a negative error code on error.

SINCE
       2.10.0

REPORTING BUGS
       Report bugs to <bugs@gnutls.org>.
       Home page: https://www.gnutls.org

